== 遊戲玩法 ==
該遊戲的玩法類似《[[质量效应系列|质量效应]]》，但含有「外星色情」元素，強調色情互動<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/4/30/18524298/studiofow-subverse-kickstarter-steam|title=Sex game that looks like a kinky Mass Effect blows up on Kickstarter|first=Patricia|last=Hernandez|date=2019-04-30|website=Polygon.com|accessdate=2019-05-06|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130184135/https://www.polygon.com/2019/4/30/18524298/studiofow-subverse-kickstarter-steam|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/we-just-wanted-to-make-dick-lasers-and-big-bouncy-anime-titties-says-creators-of-latest-kickstarter-hit/|title='We just wanted to make dick lasers and big bouncy anime titties,' says creator of latest Kickstarter hit|first=Samuel|last=Roberts|date=2019-05-03|website=Pcgamer.com|accessdate=2019-05-06|archive-date=2019-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506090947/https://www.pcgamer.com/we-just-wanted-to-make-dick-lasers-and-big-bouncy-anime-titties-says-creators-of-latest-kickstarter-hit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但在遊戲發行後，評論家認為當中的色情場景明顯缺乏任何承諾的互動體驗<ref>{{cite web|url=https://f95zone.to/threads/subverse-v0-1-studio-fow.77900/br-reviews|title=Subverse [v0.1] [Studio Fow] Reviews|website=F95Zone|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2021-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329080617/https://f95zone.to/threads/subverse-v0-1-studio-fow.77900/br-reviews|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
遙遠宇宙角落的預兆（{{lang|en|Prodigium}}）星系由五大星雲組成，分別為：龍星雲（{{lang|en|Dragon Nebula}}，帝國根據地）；九頭蛇星雲（{{lang|en|Hydra Nebula}}，克洛伊的故鄉）；克拉肯星雲（{{lang|en|Kraken nebula}}，妮基絲和凡娜拉的故鄉）；雪人星雲（{{lang|en|Yeti Nebula}}，泰利的故鄉）；以及葛里芬星雲（{{lang|en|Griffin Nebula}}，由囚禁人員建立的殖民地）。劇情圍繞於男主角「艦長」（{{lang|en|Captain}}），隨著故事進展，他與他的女機器人助手{{lang|en|DEMI}}隨其他加入瑪麗·賽勒斯特艦（{{lang|en|Mary Celeste}}）的新兵合力推翻統治銀河系的帝國。

== 開發和發行 ==
《{{lang|en|Subverse}}》是色情電腦動畫公司[[Studio_FOW|Studio FOW]]遊戲部門FOW互動（{{lang|en|FOW Interactive}}）的首款商業遊戲。截至2019年5月24日，在[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]上進行眾籌的資金已在一個月內籌集了超過160萬英鎊，使該遊戲成為迄今為止Kickstarter融資額排名前20的遊戲行列。<ref name="auto"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-05-01-sci-fi-sex-game-subverse-passes-1-5m-on-kickstarter|title=Sci-fi sex game Subverse passes £1.5m on Kickstarter|website=GamesIndustry.biz|accessdate=2019-05-06|archive-date=2019-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506202158/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-05-01-sci-fi-sex-game-subverse-passes-1-5m-on-kickstarter|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/mass-effect-inspired-porn-game-is-now-one-of-the-biggest-gaming-kickstarter-of-all-time/|title=Mass Effect-inspired porn game is now one of the biggest gaming Kickstarters of all time|first=Wes|last=Fenlon|date=2019-04-30|publisher=PC Gamer|accessdate=2019-05-06|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107231631/https://www.pcgamer.com/mass-effect-inspired-porn-game-is-now-one-of-the-biggest-gaming-kickstarter-of-all-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailydot.com/parsec/subverse-porn-game-kickstarter/|title=This alien porn game just became one of Kickstarter's greatest successes|date=2019-05-01|website=The Daily Dot|accessdate=2019-05-06|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118042430/https://www.dailydot.com/parsec/subverse-porn-game-kickstarter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最初定於2019年5月或6月發行搶先體驗版，但官方最終放棄該版本，他們僱用了經驗豐富的開發人員並接受建議，維護此類規模遊戲的早期建模<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/990500595/subverse/description|title=Subverse by FOW Interactive Kickstarter|accessdate=2021-03-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128001816/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/990500595/subverse/description|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但由於[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情在2020年帶來的影響，官方決定在[[Steam|Steam]]上搶先發布遊戲，並分批完成章節；隨著時間的推移，章節從10增加到22章。遊戲的第一階段於2021年3月26日上架。團隊針對德國、韓國、中國以及所有其他不支援Steam下載《{{lang|en|Subverse}}》的地區，創建了自己的平台網站——{{lang|en|Streemster}}，這些地區的Kickstarter支持者能在此贖回他們的Steam密鑰並免費下載遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://streemster.com/|title=Streemster|work=Streemster.com|accessdate=2021-03-28|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326182036/https://streemster.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 反響 ==
發行當週末，《{{lang|en|Subverse}}》在Steam銷售排行榜上名列第二，僅次於《{{le|瓦爾海姆 (遊戲)|Valheim|瓦爾海姆}}》<ref name="Adams2021">{{cite web |last1=Adams |first1=Robert N. |title=Stellar 'Subverse' Sales Secure #2 Spot on Steam |url=https://techraptor.net/gaming/news/stellar-subverse-sales-secure-2-spot-on-steam |website=TechRaptor |access-date=2021-04-03 |language=en |date=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410085537/https://techraptor.net/gaming/news/stellar-subverse-sales-secure-2-spot-on-steam }}</ref><ref name="Young2021">{{cite web |last1=Young |first1=Rory |title=Adults-Only Game Subverse Climbs Steam's Weekly Top-Sellers List |url=https://gamerant.com/adults-game-subverse-climbs-steams-weekly-top-sellers-list/ |website=Game Rant |access-date=2021-04-03 |date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410085537/https://gamerant.com/adults-game-subverse-climbs-steams-weekly-top-sellers-list/ }}</ref>。

由於遊戲沒有提供中文，使許多中國玩家表達了對官方中文翻譯的期望。據官方統計，絕大多數中國遊戲玩家「翻牆」至香港和台灣購買遊戲。2021年11月，官方發表聲明回應，儘管已收到相關反饋，但「成人內容在中國並不合法」，以避免對遊戲造成不利的影響為優先考量。雖然Studio FOW有意在亞洲地區推廣《{{lang|en|Subverse}}》，但在Steam上卻遭受來自中國玩家的抨擊而收穫大量負評；其中留言者聲稱該國是遊戲在眾籌階段的主力貢獻者。<ref name="LevelUp(2021-11-15)">{{cite news|url=https://www.levelup.com/noticias/650213/Jugadores-chinos-arremeten-contra-un-juego-porno-y-hacen-review-bombing-en-Steam|title=Jugadores chinos arremeten contra un juego porno y hacen review bombing en Steam|last=Contreras|first=Ulises|work=LevelUp|date=2021-11-15|accessdate=2021-11-18|archive-date=2021-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118094848/https://www.levelup.com/noticias/650213/Jugadores-chinos-arremeten-contra-un-juego-porno-y-hacen-review-bombing-en-Steam}}</ref><ref name="4Gamers(2021-11-11)">{{cite news|url=https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/50798/subverse-suffer-backlash-from-china-players-suddenly-due-to-a-reply|title=成人遊戲《Subverse》太老實說「中國流量為0」，Steam評價遭中國玩家怒洗負評|author=歪力|work=[[4Gamers|4Gamers]]|date=2021-11-11|accessdate=2021-11-18|archive-date=2021-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118094826/https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/50798/subverse-suffer-backlash-from-china-players-suddenly-due-to-a-reply}}</ref>

